# SwiftUI Patterns

- View decomposition: extract subviews when body exceeds ~30 lines
- @ViewBuilder for conditional content; avoid AnyView
- .task {} for async on appear; .refreshable {} for pull-to-refresh
- #Preview with realistic mock data
- No state in View; ViewModel holds state
- Avoid GeometryReader unless measuring
